    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《管人痴的五夜后宫》是一款注重资金管理的生存恐怖游戏。在日薪只有￥100的情况下单推了十个主播，你要如何分配给每个主播的礼物和自己的生活成本？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为什么在直播间不理我？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/b3b4a2d36d9bc611e49a02e9bc12e064.poster.avif?t=1729771904\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/b3b4a2d36d9bc611e49a02e9bc12e064.webm?t=1729771904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>记得及时交朋友费，维持你们爱情的新鲜感。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我已经毕业了，你也不会再看虚拟主播了吧？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/ebeb6d8216c3be63c920fb549eab5b60.poster.avif?t=1729771904\" width=300 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/ebeb6d8216c3be63c920fb549eab5b60.webm?t=1729771904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/ebeb6d8216c3be63c920fb549eab5b60.mp4?t=1729771904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住，她一直与你同在，注意你的言行举止。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为什么？为什么出现在别人的直播间？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/3787fba36dd265813a5a045405cd1d57.poster.avif?t=1729771904\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/3787fba36dd265813a5a045405cd1d57.webm?t=1729771904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意，女生间的贴贴，不代表她们愿意共享你的爱。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高达十个风格迥异，但同样地雷的虚拟主播。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义关卡，可以悠闲的看直播，亦可以体验拆弹专家的紧张感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肉鸽模式，在游戏过程中逐渐探索地雷妹妹的警戒线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113490/extras/_%RHE_YDU_@_YJ550US3KH1.png?t=1729771904\" /></span></p>",
